summary: Adds the two most famous Gods of Runescape: Saradomin and Zamorak, as FOLLOWERS!
descriptionHtml: While battling, the two gods of Gielinor traveled from land to land. Losing their Godly Power somewhat in the land of Tamriel, they had to stop their battle, and try to find a way out of the land of Tamriel, and back to Gielinor.
author: Darskul
